    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">A Hands-Free Solution</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The Virtual Music Stand is a PDF reader designed specifically for musicians using XR headsets. It places your sheet music on a virtual stand in your real-world space, allowing for hands-free viewing and interaction. This project aims to free the musician's hands and focus, creating a seamless bridge between digital scores and physical performance.</p>
    
