    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">This project is **coming soon** and will be **open source**. We believe in abundance through technology, and that music reading and education should be available to all that seek it. By providing powerful tools for free, we hope to empower the next generation of musicians and creators.</p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">Development Journey</h2>
    <p>This project began over five years ago as an experiment in AR sheet music readers on the **Microsoft HoloLens 2**, using the **Mixed Reality Toolkit (MRTK)**. The initial prototypes proved the concept of a stable, world-locked virtual music stand. Today, development is focused on the **Meta Quest 3** and future standalone XR devices, rebuilding the application with modern tools to create a more robust, user-friendly, and accessible tool for all musicians.</p>
